B044C004V009	44	4	9	If we are being questioned today for a good deed to someone who was sick or to learn how this man was healed,
B044C004V010	44	4	10	you and all the people of Israel must understand that this man stands healthy before you because of the name of Jesus from Nazareth, whom you crucified but God raised from the dead.
B044C004V011	44	4	11	He is	‘the stone that was rejected by you builders,which has become the cornerstone.’
B044C004V012	44	4	12	There is no salvation by anyone else, for there is no other name under heaven given among people by which we must be saved.”
