B044C004V037	44	4	37	sold a field that belonged to him and brought the money and laid it at the apostles’ feet.
B044C005V001	44	5	1	But a man named Ananias, with the consent of his wife Sapphira, sold some property.
B044C005V002	44	5	2	With his wife's full knowledge he kept back some of the money for himself and brought only a part of it and laid it at the apostles’ feet.
B044C005V003	44	5	3	Peter asked, “Ananias, why has Satan filled your heart so that you should lie to the Holy Spirit and keep back some of the money you got for the land?
B044C005V004	44	5	4	As long as it remained unsold, wasn't it your own? And after it was sold, wasn't the money at your disposal? So how could you have conceived such a thing in your heart? You did not lie to men but to God!”
