B044C005V023	44	5	23	“We found the prison securely locked and the guards standing at the doors, but when we opened them, we found no one inside.”
B044C005V024	44	5	24	When the commander of the temple guards and the high priests heard these words, they were utterly at a loss as to what could have happened to them.
B044C005V025	44	5	25	Then someone came and told them, “Look! The men you put in prison are standing in the temple and teaching the people!”
