B044C008V001	44	8	1	Now Saul heartily approved of putting him to death. That day a severe persecution broke out against the church in Jerusalem, and all of them, except for the apostles, were scattered throughout the countryside of Judea and Samaria.
B044C008V002	44	8	2	Devout men buried Stephen as they mourned loudly for him.
B044C008V003	44	8	3	But Saul kept trying to destroy the church. Going into one house after another, he began dragging off men and women and throwing them in prison.
