B044C008V027	44	8	27	So he got up and went. Now an Ethiopian eunuch was there. He was a member of the court of Candace, queen of the Ethiopians, and was in charge of all her treasures. He had come to Jerusalem to worship
B044C008V028	44	8	28	and was returning home. He was seated in his chariot, reading the prophet Isaiah.
