B044C010V011	44	10	11	and saw heaven open and something like a large linen sheet coming down, being lowered by its four corners to the ground.
B044C010V012	44	10	12	In it were all kinds of four-footed animals, reptiles, and birds of the air.
B044C010V013	44	10	13	Then a voice told him,
