B044C010V018	44	10	18	They called out and asked if Simon who was called Peter was staying there.
B044C010V019	44	10	19	Peter was still thinking about the vision when the Spirit said to him, “Look! Three men are looking for you.
B044C010V020	44	10	20	Get up, go downstairs, and don't hesitate to go with them, for I have sent them.”
