B044C010V022	44	10	22	The men replied, “Cornelius, a centurion and an upright and God-fearing man who is respected by the whole Jewish nation, was instructed by a holy angel to send for you to come to his home to hear what you have to say.”
B044C010V023	44	10	23	So Peter invited them in, and they were his guests. The next day he got up and went with them, and some of the brothers from Joppa went along with him.
