B044C010V030	44	10	30	Cornelius replied, “Four days ago at this very hour, three o'clock in the afternoon, I was praying in my home. All at once a man in radiant clothes stood in front of me
B044C010V031	44	10	31	and said, ‘Cornelius, your prayer has been heard and your gifts to the poor have been remembered before God.
B044C010V032	44	10	32	So send messengers to Joppa and summon Simon, who is called Peter, to come to you. He is a guest in the home of Simon, a leatherworker, by the sea.’
