B044C010V042	44	10	42	He also ordered us to preach to the people and to testify solemnly that this is the one ordained by God to be the judge of the living and the dead.
B044C010V043	44	10	43	To him all the prophets testify that everyone who believes in him receives the forgiveness of sins through his name.”
